  ## Paragraph & Inline Styles                                                
                                                                              
  This is a regular paragraph with **bold text**, *italic text*, and *bold    
  italic text*. You can also use ~~strikethrough~~ for deleted content. Inline
  code appears within a sentence like this.                                   
                                                                              
  --------                                                                    
                                                                              
  ## Blockquote                                                               
                                                                              
  | This is a blockquote. It can span multiple lines and contain other        
  | elements.                                                                 
  |                                                                           
  | It can have multiple paragraphs, and even **bold** or *italic* text inside.
  |                                                                           
  | | Nested blockquotes are also supported.                                  
                                                                              
  --------                                                                    
                                                                              
